title: Demons & Grumpy Ghosts Feat. Joe DeRosa | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 47
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
The babes are back on the couch in studio and ready to serve up some TEA. This episode the babes get into the Halloween spirit!! Demons and even a special appearance from A VERY GRUMP GHOST! Joe DeRosa joins the program once Chris has to run to pick up his kids from school.
